    <div class="fund-item">★ 5.1 Financial Management, Responsibility &amp; Accountability</div>
    <div class="fund-item">★ 5.2 Legal Authority and Fiscal Policy</div>
    <div class="fund-item">★ 5.3 Comprehensive Revenue Policy</div>
    <div class="fund-item">★ 5.5 Financial Statements</div>
